  "_comment": "MD coverage policy is regulatory: COMAR Title 10 Subtitle 09 has ~90 per-service chapters. dsd.maryland.gov/regulations/Pages/10.09.NN.01.aspx 301-redirects to regs.maryland.gov (per-section HTML; chapter-index .00 path 404s after redirect, so link sections). Provider-manual PDFs are scattered across /mmcp/ sub-sites — the Provider Information page lists fee schedules + manuals; Community Support Services hosts DME/DMS approved-list. Pharmacy program at /mmcp/pap. NEMT is administered via local health departments (no FFS billing manual). HealthChoice MCO manuals (Aetna/CareFirst/etc) skipped — payer-specific.",
